    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieves Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; this gap is accepted given the conservative quasi-static loading assumption and the corroborating multi-laboratory experimental dataset. All three QoIs satisfy pre-specified quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96; percentage difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is judged credible for the intended regulatory use. Note: aleatory uncertainty in the force-at-40mm validation result was assessed qualitatively only; a structured UQ characterization was not completed for that result prior to submission.",
